*hal-0.2.97 (17 Aug 2004)

  17 Aug 2004; foser <foser@gentoo.org> hal-0.2.97.ebuild, metadata.xml, Changelog :
  Initial commit of hal (Hardware Abstraction Layer), a layer on top of udev to get hardware info
